@startuml
title VoterSystem Android - Architecture Overview
left to right direction
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

actor User
actor "External Login Provider" as Provider
component "MainActivity" as MainActivity
component "VoterSystemApp" as App
component "AppNavigator\n(screen + error state)" as Navigator
component "Auth Screens\nAuthLandingScreen\nLoginScreen\nRegisterScreen" as AuthScreens
component "Voting Screens\nVotingListScreen\nVotingDetailScreen\nVotingHistoryScreen" as VotingScreens
component "ErrorPopup" as ErrorPopup
component "Api" as Api
component "Server\nOkHttp + token refresh" as Server
component "SessionStore\nsecure local tokens" as SessionStore
component "SignalRClient" as SignalR
database "REST Backend" as Backend

User --> MainActivity : launch app
MainActivity --> App : setContent()
App --> Navigator : reads current screen
App --> AuthScreens : renders auth flow
App --> VotingScreens : renders voting flow
Navigator --> ErrorPopup : exposes error popup state

AuthScreens --> Api : login / register / current user
VotingScreens --> Api : list / detail / vote / history
VotingScreens --> SignalR : live result updates
Api --> Server : execute requests
Server --> SessionStore : load/save/clear tokens
Server --> Backend : HTTPS requests
SignalR --> Backend : results hub

AuthScreens --> Provider : browser-based external login
Provider --> MainActivity : deep link callback
MainActivity --> Api : request sign-in tokens
MainActivity --> Navigator : open VotingList or show error

note bottom of Server
Owns auth state and retries once
through refresh-token when a request gets 401.
end note

skinparam shadowing false

Open --> AuthLanding

AuthLanding --> VotingList : stored session is valid
AuthLanding --> LoginForm : Login
AuthLanding --> RegisterForm : Register
AuthLanding --> ExternalBrowser : Google / Facebook / Neptun
ExternalBrowser --> AuthCallback : deep link
AuthCallback --> VotingList : tokens accepted
AuthCallback --> AuthLanding : admin or failed login

RegisterForm --> LoginForm : successful registration
RegisterForm --> AuthLanding : Back

LoginForm --> VotingList : login success
LoginForm --> LoginForm : 2FA challenge / validation error
LoginForm --> AuthLanding : Back

VotingList --> VotingDetail : select voting
VotingList --> VotingHistory : History
VotingList --> AuthLanding : Logout

VotingDetail --> VotingHistory : vote submitted
VotingDetail --> VotingList : Back

VotingHistory --> VotingList : Voting
VotingHistory --> AuthLanding : Logout

note right of VotingHistory
Subscribes to SignalR for live result updates.
end note

@enduml
